## Additional Healthcare Notice

This software is designed for health management and wellness tracking purposes. 
While we strive for accuracy and reliability, this software:

- Is not intended to replace professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment
- Should not be used for emergency medical situations
- Users should always consult with qualified healthcare professionals
- Is provided for informational and educational purposes

By using this software, you acknowledge that the authors and contributors are 
not liable for any health-related decisions made based on the software's output.

---

## Open Source Commitment

Akasi.ai is committed to democratizing healthcare technology. This project is 
released under the MIT License to ensure:

- Healthcare organizations can adopt and modify the software freely
- Individuals can self-host for personal health management
- Researchers and developers can build upon our work
- Communities can deploy health management solutions without barriers

We encourage contributions, feedback, and collaborative development to improve 
healthcare accessibility for everyone, especially those managing chronic conditions.

For questions about this license or collaboration opportunities, please contact:
- Team Akasi.ai via GitHub Issues
- Healthcare partnerships: emmanuel.irogirog@gmail.com or jenricaanndecafe@gmail.com